    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尊敬的各位玩家冒险者们：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们是群小小的独立游戏开发人员，我们在尝试用一些不同的方式制作独立游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>虽然经历了一些磨难，但是我们仍然在努力。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入我们的玩家社群和QQ官方群，告诉我们对这款游戏的想法和意见。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一位玩家的建议、思路、以及愤怒，我们都会认真对待，它们都拥有极高的价值，是我们迭代更新的重要依据和参考。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[七度荒域-混沌之树]玩家Q群：572433049</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ac6ae064dcbc78d251af6e509c1fee11.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>ACT之名打造极致2D像素类战斗体验!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/2f666634c73842e82d033d42a81094f6.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>这世界提供多样化武器与技能的搭配，每种搭配都可以带来不同的策略和战斗体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>同时也结合了横版动作游戏的特性，来为这世界创造秘密。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/54f38815ef8c1f02f288480a19c62a38.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Rogue类刷宝收集是猎人的最爱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这世界提供繁多的装备词缀，可以组装成各种不同的属性战术方式。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用这样的机制取代来致敬剑与魔法时代的追求。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/930c77017c4f63d891870d7fde2144df.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>这个世界拥有等级，也拥有重复死亡，这样的前进方式，需要你我的追寻。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在致敬也是在前进。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/7d7bc7d525293124398d1519901dcc8c.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=108 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.poster.avif?t=1755056182\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.webm?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.mp4?t=1755056182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>可以组装成不同的属性和战术方法。取而代之的是</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>传统天赋装备粘贴构建与搭配、有趣的事件线索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与神秘的回声卡牌、3D像素变换技术于一体</strong></p>",
